text: David Browne (born 4 April 1964) is an English cricketer. He played eight first-class matches for Cambridge University Cricket Club between 1985 and 1986. ==See also== * List of Cambridge University Cricket Club players ==References== ==External links== * Category:1964 births Category:Living people Category:English cricketers Category:Cambridge University cricketers Category:People from Stamford, Lincolnshire
